==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Spawner
<hw>Spawn"er</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <sn>1.</sn>
<fld>(Zool.)</fld> <def>A mature female fish.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>The barbel, for the preservation or their seed, both the
<qex>spawner</qex> and the milter, cover their spawn with sand.</q>
<rj><qau>Walton.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>Whatever produces spawn of any kind.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Spay</ent>⟦br⟧
